    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
