    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E92 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering featuring the S65 4.0L V8 powerplant. This high-revving unit utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS high-pressure stepless variable valve timing to achieve a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a GKN-sourced variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The suspension retains its factory-fresh kinematics with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing instantaneous damping adjustment. The exterior maintains original paint depth across all panels, with zero evidence of stone peppering or heat-cycle stress on the carbon fiber roof's clear coat. This is a mechanically synchronized, collector-grade example of BMW M\u2019s final naturally aspirated V8.",
